SUMMARY:Lec1|Software and Algorithmic Approaches to Quantum Noise Mitigation: An Overview|Yongshan Ding-Yale
LOCATION:https://tinyurl.com/gucs-zoom
DESCRIPTION:I will talk about recent developments in noise mitigation techniques for quantum computers. In the Noisy Intermediate-Scale Quantum (NISQ) era\, qubits have short lifetimes and quantum gates are prone to errors. This talk will provide an overview of software and algorithmic approaches to mitigate quantum noise.
